						<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Featuring the professional sewing techniques of high quality real leather corsets.</li>
<li>4 types of decoration for 4 different front pieces.</li>
<li>The sewing technique of the corset with changeable front part.</li>
<li>Working with metal accessories in corset making.</li>
<li>Working with special equipment for leather.</li>
<li>Specialties of fitting the leather garment.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Skills you gain:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Decorating the garment with 4 techniques: 2D applique, 3D applique, machine embroidery and rivets and snaps decoration.</li>
<li>Sewing the corset from the real leather material.</li>
<li>Cutting the leather.</li>
<li>Working with metal flat boning, spiral boning and metal busk.</li>
<li>Duplicating the leather with iron-on batiste.</li>
<li>Calculation and alteration of the&nbsp;pattern for leather under-bust corset.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Where to use:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Sewing corsets and other garments from real leather.</li>
<li>Making steampunk, gothic and other styles corsets.</li>
